{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on August 8, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "do not buy", "Text": "This was a HUGE disappointment. Worked great when it first arrived and even considered buying more bulbs for the rest of my house. However, after like two months this product seemed to stop working with my alexa I tried literally everything but it remained a disappointment. Do not waste your money on this. Seriously, don't."}
