{"Author": "RunnerGirlDE", "Date": "on August 4, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I love being about to ask the lights to be dimmed ...", "Text": "My husband and I no longer fight over who needs to get out bed to turn the bedroom lights on or off. We simply ask Alexa and it's done. I love being about to ask the lights to be dimmed and since they are in a ceiling fan with 3 bulbs I can ask Alexa to turn off specific bulbs if I go to sleep before my husband."}
