{"Author": "johnathan m", "Date": "on July 21, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Ease of use and quality product.", "Text": "I love all the Hue products. I have the hub color lights and regular white as well. I would recommend everyone buy these. One thing though if you have a sensor light switch like my old apartment did, if you can't set the sensor to always use the switch instead of the sensor then this set-up will not work. The switches in my old apartment would just cut the power after so long and the settings had no way to turn that off.."}
{"Author": "Abhishek D.", "Date": "on July 20, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I would recommend this product. The setup is easy", "Text": "I bought this product for my bedroom. The setup is very easy. But to connect it with google home, first you need to unlink any previous bridges if connected and then link this bridge. I faced issues in adding this hue bridge to google home mini as I had another bridge already linked(which I returned)."}
