{"Author": "Lee", "Date": "on July 18, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Works great. I'm bummed the hub isn't WiFi because it's ...", "Text": "Works great. I'm bummed the hub isn't WiFi because it's annoying to have plugged in via hard wire. But it works like described and is nice to have dimmable lights. I integrated into Alexa and she controls the lights and the dimming function very well."}
