{"Author": "David Horning", "Date": "on July 10, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I love these bulbs for reading lights", "Text": "I hate getting up in the middle of the night to turn off my reading light! Being able to adjust the light with the dimmer funtion makes ot so I'm not bothering other people if I'm up later than they are. I'm planning on getting more bulbs and converting my whole home so I can turn on and off whole rooms with a tap of a button!"}
