{"Author": "Douglas Y.", "Date": "on July 4, 2018", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Color too soft for me.", "Text": "I think the lights are too yellow. Seems softer than old fashioned incandescent lamps - surprised i am not seeing others comment on this, but if you want white, look elsewhere. I was looking at these for the living room, dining room and kitchen, and these won't work for me. Everything with the kit worked wonderful - easy to set up, worked seamlessly with Alexa - I am just disappointed with the color. (image shows contrasting white light)."}
