{"Author": "JDee", "Date": "on May 7, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Google Assistant works PERFECT!", "Text": "Such a great product. Set it up one time and have never had a single issue since we set it up. Works every single time perfectly with my Google Home and Google Home mini."}
{"Author": "Juan L. Rodriguez", "Date": "on May 7, 2018", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "It's not as useful as it could be", "Text": "It's ok. It's not as useful as it could be. I find that even when we set the rules for when we want lights to turn on, they aren't always followed. The systems seems to need weekly updates. It can be convenient, but seems to be more trouble than it's really worth."}
{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on May 6, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Absolutely horrible!!", "Text": "Absolutely horrible!!!! If I could give negative stars, I would. I paid the $40 for the white and color ambiance bulb. It was never even recognized.... pointless. The other bulb (as I only tried one) worked with your phone...but not with speaking. It would not even work with Alexa... which was the whole idea of me getting this. There is NO support number anywhere on the crappy, so called instructions. There is also NO number for support on their app that I saw. This is one of the most expensive and horrible products that I have ever purchased. DO NOT BUY THIS!!!!"}
