{"Author": "JL", "Date": "on April 22, 2018", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Very good", "Text": "Received a smart speaker as a gift and decide to give these smart bulbs a try. It is really nice to set up timers, turn on/off and dim/brighten my lights without having to touch the switch. Although I would've like it if it can get even dimmer than what it is currently capable of. I have found that it works best with stand alone lamps in individual rooms and also exterior porch lights. Definitely will look for more of these to expand my smart home lighting."}
