{"Author": "snipes", "Date": "on April 13, 2018", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Would be better if they would remember the last setting they were ...", "Text": "Would be better if they would remember the last setting they were on once you turn them on and off from the switch."}
