{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on April 13, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "They work very well with the Dot and is nice to adjust the lighting well beyond the normal on ...", "Text": "This was bought for us in addition to an Echo Dot. They work very well with the Dot and is nice to adjust the lighting well beyond the normal on / off."}
{"Author": "Stan Lee", "Date": "on April 12, 2018", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I have really liked these. I just hate that they cost so ...", "Text": "I have really liked these. I just hate that they cost so much. That is the only reason for the lack of a fifth star. I am more into these for the function they provide to the home and have not tried exploring the Scenes yet. The safety aspect of having the lights turn on and off on their own while on vaca or the ability to walk into a fully lite house is a great peace of mind."}
{"Author": "RVS", "Date": "on April 12, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Worked great, we prefer this over TP-LINK's KASA!", "Text": "We originally purchased this after purchasing our Alexa unit and could not be more pleased! Some people may despise the fact that there is a separate hub for all of your devices, but I personally prefer the hub as I have had experience with wireless lights such as TP-LINK's KASA which just never seems to want to sync up with Alexa. We ultimately had to throw them away because they would not do as they were intended.\nPhilips is a brand that I trust wholeheartedly and this product was something that simply did not disappoint. We have since gone on and purchased several accessories to use throughout the house, allowing us to create quite the efficient little Smart Home, all with the help of the Philips Hue collection!\nIf you're purchasing this, I highly recommend looking at the other products that they have to offer from the Hue collection!"}
{"Author": "DaringOne", "Date": "on April 12, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Pairing this setup with Alexa has been awesome. This kit (when I bought it) cost less ...", "Text": "Pairing this setup with Alexa has been awesome. This kit (when I bought it) cost less than a standard four bulb kit, and included the hub. Can't ask for more value than that!"}
