{"Author": "Jim in SoDak", "Date": "on March 31, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Perfect for my Smart Home", "Text": "This works seamlessly with my Amazon Echo and my Google Home, it also works great with the Google Assistant on my Android phone. I have placed the two bulbs in very strategic locations in my home so that it makes going to bed a lot easier and I'm not having to play the light switch game. It's nice that with the Hue app you can set an alarm to have the light gradually turn on when you wake up. It's much less of a startling wake up than an alarm clock. For anybody that's working on the Smart Home scene, I highly recommend it."}
