{"Author": "Anthony S.", "Date": "on March 31, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Easy of integration and love the white hue. Value for money as a starter kit.", "Text": "Great buy for the price. Got this together with the 4-pack set and it was fantastic. Love the soft colour and the ease with which this works with Alexa and Homekit. No problems whatsoever controlling these via the app and voice. Steady, rock solid network connection and the size of the bulb is perfect for all sorts of standard installations. I would highly recommend this if you do to need to change the hue of the white bulb to cool daylight, etc."}
{"Author": "Ashley", "Date": "on March 30, 2018", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Cuts on and off randomly!", "Text": "These lights will cut on and off randomly! It freaks me out! I have read multiple articles on this, they say that there might be a routine that is set for a certain time, but I've checked on my routine list and I have none. Other than this issue.. I like my lights. I love that I can control them with my Alexa or with the Hue app."}
{"Author": "A. Hanes", "Date": "on March 29, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Five Stars", "Text": "great"}
{"Author": "cardboardmoney", "Date": "on March 29, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Don't work and help hotline dosent exist", "Text": "They have a nice look to them, now if only I could actually connect them to the hub that came with it. First it comes with them pre programmed and it said all lights were unreachable so I tried trouble shooting everything. Nothing worked so I tried deleting the bulbs from the app and adding them back. But now it can't find them at all and to add them manually you need the serial number that's supposed to be on the bulb but the 4 that CAME WITH THE STARTER PACK don't even have #s on them. After finally biting the bullet on smart lighting I think I'm gonna go back to regular lights that don't waste 90 dollars. I even called the support number on the side and couldn't even get a connection with them, IM DONE. The pictures I added is one of the bulbs that came with the kit."}
{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on March 29, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Fun way to light your home", "Text": "Excellent. So far so good. I am not sure yet of course how long these bulbs will last only time will tell. They connected to the bridge and updated without trouble and I was able to set up so my lights come on at certain times and turn off too. One of my kids flipped the light switch and messed it up, but it was easy to reset it in the Hue app. Can't wait to get more lights to go with this."}
