{"Author": "D. Somers", "Date": "on March 27, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great for that", "Text": "I have a number of these in rooms where I want control of lights without having to run to a switch. Great for that. Otherwise I don't get too excited over smart appliances. I do wish they made brighter versions of these however."}
