{"Author": "Samantha", "Date": "on March 19, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "... home and I've started the transition to all things smart and this was the perfect kit for setting up ...", "Text": "We just moved into our first home and I've started the transition to all things smart and this was the perfect kit for setting up our first smart lights. We use these in our bedroom and living room and there is nothing as satisfying as not having to get out of bed once you're comfortable for the night just to turn off the lights. Super easy to set up and use. Will be purchasing more!"}
