{"Author": "James C. Kellett", "Date": "on February 13, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Total ripoff! Non-funcrtional product, no product support", "Text": "Installation instructions ridiculous and incomplete. Purchased to connect to Echo, no instructions on how to do that OR which app to use, or even if one is needed for this kind of use! Phillips provides ZERO customer support, email to them went unanswered (other than to put me on a product mailing list!!) After finally figuring out how to install, completed the installation - twice! - but could get only two of the four lights to function."}
