{"Author": "Kelly M. Leicher", "Date": "on February 11, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Philips Hue Bulbs are simply brilliant. If you're an apartment dweller and don't have ...", "Text": "Philips Hue Bulbs are simply brilliant. If you're an apartment dweller and don't have the ability to hard-wire dimmer switches, these bulbs solve that problem AND add the \"wow factor\" of being fully controlled by voice via a smart hub like the Amazon Echo. You can schedule wake up and bed times, as well as a geocaching feature that turns off all of the lights when you leave with your smart phone. If you're embracing the future, these bulbs are fantastic!"}
