{"Author": "Kwebbster", "Date": "on February 7, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Smart Home Lighting Made Easy!", "Text": "These are the perfect addition to any smart home! They integrate well with the Amazon Echo and the app for Hue works quite well. It has made our lives much easier by entering a room and asking Alexa to turn on and off the light. You can also set levels of brightness this way. The Hue app allows you to schedule times and events to turn lights on and off. The bridge is pretty small and we have it linked via Ethernet for stability. If you are interested in smart home things or want your Amazon Echo to do more than just answer questions, this is the one to buy."}
