{"Author": "Dedric", "Date": "on January 25, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great as a starter kit.", "Text": "Great as a starter kit. I use these with the Harmon Kardon Invoke w/Cortana and I have had no problems. This kit works well with Home Remote for Windows 10 and I am able to control the lights while I'm away from home. This is my first smart home project but I'm looking to expand with other lights."}
