{"Author": "Kara", "Date": "on January 17, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Didn't know the switches have to remain on. If ...", "Text": "Didn't know the switches have to remain on. If they are in the standard off position it will say \"not reachable\" on the Hue app. So far i haven't been able to link it with my xfinity home which was the whole reason i bought it but it works through its own app for what i need it to. I may consider getting an Alexa. Idk yet"}
