{"Author": "Felyppe", "Date": "on January 15, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great product with great features!", "Text": "The product itself is great, only had a few issues with the communication between the hubs and the bulbs, but after a reset on the system the problem went away."}
{"Author": "hwanjaengi", "Date": "on January 15, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "for people who feel bothered to turn off the light right before sleeping!", "Text": "I bought with the Echo dot and haven't checked the connectivity, but by itself with a mobile, it worked perfectly.\nWithout inconvenience, you can turn off your light with a phone!"}
{"Author": "Jessica Inman", "Date": "on January 15, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Working well for me!", "Text": "I love these bulbs. I use them with the Echo Dot. You will probably only need one hub per household (a hub is good for about 40 smart bulbs). The setup was not hard on my iPhone 6s. I\u2019d recommend these bulbs."}
{"Author": "Carrie K,", "Date": "on January 15, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Very happy with these bulbs and the hub", "Text": "Very happy with these bulbs and the hub. Works great with Alexa. Have some set up in a group and set to come on before I arrive home. Nice coming home to a well lit home rather than a dark home. Just wish they could make a bulb that works in enclosed fixtures and could work in outside fixtures. Maybe one day they will."}
