{"Author": "Buckeye", "Date": "on December 30, 2017", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Received this for Christmas and I liked the idea", "Text": "Received this for Christmas and I liked the idea. The problem is that is is very difficult to set up. There are no instructions with this and no place on line that gives instructions. Philips needs to hire some software engineers to simplify the process. I also have two TP-LINK smart plugs from amazon that are hands above these Philips bulbs."}
{"Author": "#1Amazon Cstomr#1.$", "Date": "on December 30, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Five Stars", "Text": "Black Friday bundle amazing for the price good place to start when building a smart home"}
