{"Author": "Leon", "Date": "on December 26, 2017", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Disappointed!", "Text": "Before buying I asked if this product works with Arlo Security cameras via IFTTT. Everything is set up, unforrtunately the Hue lights can not be connected in the IFTTT app. Disappointed !"}
