{"Author": "Jennie", "Date": "on December 8, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Love it!", "Text": "Love these! I set up 2 bulbs & the hub for my parents to use with HomeKit on their iPhones. I took the other 2 bulbs home and synced it easily with my hub using the serial numbers. Love controlling the lights from the comfort of my bed. We have timers so we waste less electricity. Great buy."}
