{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on December 8, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "These are a game changer!", "Text": "I have a newborn baby so having these lights is a lifesaver. When I have my hands full or I\u2019m holding her it\u2019s hard to simply turn the lights on or off especially if I\u2019m putting her to sleep so to have Alexa do it is so convenient. Sometimes I even use my phone they work with iPhones. I want to get four more bulbs and make my entire house smart LOL what was I doing with my life before these."}
