{"Author": "Orion", "Date": "on December 3, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Make sure your smart hub (included) can connect to the router via ethernet ...", "Text": "Make sure your smart hub (included) can connect to the router via ethernet in the same room as the bulbs are installed. The smart hub will not connect to your wifi and the bulbs need to be very, very close (same room) as the smart hub. Feels like a prototype."}
{"Author": "TOM", "Date": "on December 3, 2017", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Nice packaging. Better have a lot of patience for ...", "Text": "Nice packaging. Better have a lot of patience for this product. Instructions are for the birds. Funny they spend so much on a product then leave you hanging with less to poor instructions. Also no customer service just a never ending ringing phone that no one answers. After much research and trial and error I finally got thinks working."}
