{"Author": "Cynthia Wildes", "Date": "on December 3, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Our Home Just Got Smarter!", "Text": "OMGOSH - These are Amazing! The best purchase - early Christmas gift I could have ever purchased! Even the other half thought the same. Now we can leave our home and feel safe. I love that - through new technology - our home just got smarter and more safe."}
