{"Author": "M. Crawford", "Date": "on December 2, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I have no idea whether these smart bulbs work well or not", "Text": "I have no idea whether these smart bulbs work well or not. I never got to set them up and play around with them or the app. Apparently, the hub requires not only a wall plug in, but also a physical connection to your router with an incredibly short cable. Which doesn\u2019t fit any of the slots in my router. If I\u2019d known this up front, I probably wouldn\u2019t have made this purchase. It doesn\u2019t seem very smart, and it\u2019s certainly not convenient, to require this type of connection for the hub. It should be able to connect to my WiFi via... WiFi. Right? Like the smart plug I bought. Whatever. I guess if none of my friends can use this, I\u2019ll have to return it."}
{"Author": "K. Gwydir", "Date": "on December 2, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Worked fine for a while now when I tell Alexa to ...", "Text": "Worked fine for a while now when I tell Alexa to turn them off they turn right back on - no help from Phillips"}
{"Author": "Ronald J Lee", "Date": "on December 2, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I like that I'm able to schedule the lights to come ...", "Text": "I've had the Hue system for about a year now. I like that I'm able to schedule the lights to come on and off and the fact that I can tell Alexa to turn them on and off from my couch!"}
{"Author": "Joe T", "Date": "on December 2, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Works great!", "Text": "Setup took ten minutes. Works flawlessly. We had no interest in color or operating room lights so these are great for our living rooms. The app is easy to understand and seems to be well setup. We haven't tried using the app off wifi but I'm not sure we will either. You can set any schedule you want on each individual light when home. \ud83e\udd13"}
{"Author": "Hankster", "Date": "on December 2, 2017", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Glitchy", "Text": "The setup for this product is glitchy. There is an unpleasant lag when executing a request with\nGoogle home. It is far too expensive for what it can do. I recommend that you avoid this product until the product becomes more refined and significantly cheaper. I am returning the item."}
