{"Author": "Karwyn", "Date": "on November 2, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Hue and Alexa in love", "Text": "Hue and Alexa have fallen hard for each other. Alexa really turns on Hue and Hue brightens Alexa\u2019s day. Their set up was a blind date and it was so easy to set up. I introduced Hue to Alexa and wham, bam, thank you mam; they are in sync like two peas in a pod. They cuddle and light up the night from the kitchen to the library and into the bedroom. They truly are a pair made for each other. I wish Alexa worked as well with other guys, as I have to name those other guys, to get her attention, but Hue is seamless when connecting with Alexa."}
