{"Author": "Momxyxy", "Date": "on October 16, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Waste of Money.", "Text": "I HATE THIS! First of all, this product is described as \"wireless.\" No where in the description did it mention that the hub must be DIRECTLY connected into the Router. If you are like me, your Router is full of other connections and I don't have another electrical outlet near the router. I spent days re-configuring the Router and electrical wires so that I could set up the Hub. After completing that task, the Hub would not complete the set-up (it is also required to link to your cell phone). So, this product is mis-represented. Not easy to set up and DOES NOT WORK!!!!"}
