{"Author": "Kate", "Date": "on August 13, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Nice set up...", "Text": "Okay, here's the deal: I like the smart bulb concept. I like the Phillips Hue Hub that came with them. I like being able to tell Alexa to dim the lights (20%, 50%, etc), I like that the bulbs are lightweight and sturdy. What I don't like is the shade of light offered by Phillips. I like light bulbs that offer a \"daylight\" bright setting - these bulb are a warm white or candlelight luminance. If a soft white is what you like, these will make you happy. Maybe some day I will find a Phillips Hue \"daylight\" brightness to replace the ones I own."}
