{"Author": "Tom", "Date": "on August 12, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "The Philips Hue set up was extremely easy and it easily has the most accessories built around ...", "Text": "The Philips Hue set up was extremely easy and it easily has the most accessories built around it including a dimmer switch, motion sensor, light strip, flood lights, etc. I integrated it with Homekit and Siri and everything works fairly smoothly. There are a few things that could be better, I wish the bulbs had higher lumens and the need for a hub is a negative considering other options don't require one."}
