{"Author": "Spiker", "Date": "on August 9, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Love the ability to automate, schedule and dim!", "Text": "These are great - they are my first set of \"smart\" bulbs, and I added them to the two lights we have in our bedroom. With our Alexa, it is so easy to turn lights on and off, or even dim the lights. Playing with the apps allows for random turn on/off when we are away, to make it seem like people are at the house. I can't wait to add some more, maybe even the color ones, to my living room.\n\nVery bright, at least bright enough for my needs!"}
