{"Author": "Scott D. Hanson", "Date": "on August 4, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Magic", "Text": "Works perfectly with the amazon echo. We only have these in the bedroom, but I plan to put them in more rooms. Set-up was fairly easy once I figured out that I needed to have the control box, my router and my echo all in the same room - for set up only. The last thing we say each night is, \"Alexa, turn off the lights.\" The first thing we say each morning is, \"Alexa, turn on the lights.\" Magic! The control box will handle many, many bulbs, but they cost about $15 each so I am not in a hurry to replace all the bulbs in the house. Would be nice to have in the basement, garage, front porch, master bath and living room"}
