{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on July 31, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "This Product Can Turn Into a Horror Story", "Text": "This product started out working well. After about 4 months all lightbulbs became unreachable and I was not able to get them back on line. I contacted Philips tech Support, Then had me running all over my house moving the bulbs close to the bridge and then away from the bridge. Now that they can't get them working they want me to send the product back to their lab to see if they want to issue a refund. Doing business with Philips is nothing short of a nightmare. I recommend considering my horror story before buying anything with the Philips name on it."}
