{"Author": "daisysalter", "Date": "on July 27, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Be sure to download the right app", "Text": "The product works beautifully. But download the free Phillips Hue bridge app to your phone or iPad. NOT the one that costs $6. The free one walks you through and helps the bridge and lights do everything promised. Works great with Alexa. Takes only minutes to set up. The other is useless and might set your hair on fire. You don't know any of this unless you go on line. I found the right app and help on YouTube."}
