{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on June 26, 2017", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I sure it is operator error but this project took ...", "Text": "I sure it is operator error but this project took longer to figure out then I anticipated. I misunderstood the process for sure."}
