{"Author": "C. Smitty", "Date": "on June 5, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Impress Your Guests or Your Dog", "Text": "This is a great way to get started in making your home a smart home. I started with this kit and have expanded to every light bulb in my house. It's nice that you only need one bridge for so might lights. It was so easy to set up that my managed to set on up in her house as well! Everyone who asks how I set up my own is impressed.\n\nI also have the added piece of mind of being able to use my cell phone to control my lights. This is a nice security feature! Now when I'm away on business or just running late I can turn on different lights to appear like I'm home. My dog appreciates this as well when I'm late coming home from work. Overall, I highly recommend this to everyone."}
