{"Author": "Mark C", "Date": "on May 25, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "helps my kids turn the lights off", "Text": "Hue is a great invention to add on to the house. We have a light connection that turned on two lights at same time and could not separate. By using Hue, each bulb is controlled, and now, that issue is resolved. This also helps my kids turn the lights off when the leave a room, or if they still forget, then can do it from the smart device."}
