{"Author": "Sagar Sapre", "Date": "on May 22, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I have had Alexa since long year but i never ...", "Text": "I have had Alexa since long year but i never took any more efforts to automate my home with it. I decided to get this and its sweeet! I am ordering few more to replace them with other ordinary light bulbs in the house."}
{"Author": "Haik Yegurdzhyan", "Date": "on May 20, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Works great but can be better", "Text": "Came in a timely manner, the product works great. A little disappointed with the Android app, however. It is poorly made. I cannot rename the light bulb. I had to go to the website to rename it. Works with Amazon Alexa. However, you do have to be quite specific on what you say. Fortunately, they do claim to save electricity so its worth the buy!"}
