{"Author": "Dog Judge", "Date": "on May 13, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great Products", "Text": "Very happy with this product. It is simple to install and with the excellent app it is easy to add the individual lights and then group them as I wish into different \"rooms\", each with a unique name. It lets me know when updates are available for the hub and/or the lights, which is a big advantage. While I wish the bulbs were more easily available and less expensive, I've had the hub and bulbs for several months now and I'm totally pleased with them."}
