{"Author": "KAREN DAVIS", "Date": "on May 8, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Must have if you own ECHO!", "Text": "Got this for my husband he is a gadget type of guy he loves having this item in his basement. You speak to Alexa turn on light WOW lights on/off it also has a dimmer effect pleasant surprise. Would recommend to purchase. They also sell PhIlips Hue at Best buy for $69.00 which is a few dollars more than Amazon just in case you need some extra light bulbs and don't have Amazon Prime."}
