{"Author": "Jehzeel Laurente", "Date": "on April 26, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "100% Yellow Light, not White.", "Text": "I like it. But I think I made a mistake. I thought this is \"WHITE\". But it's just warm white, so it's always yellow. I thought I can adjust it to cool white, but I can't. The only thing it does brighter or dimmer. Overall, it's working. I just made a mistake and bought it immediately without really researching online that it's just yellow light, not white."}
{"Author": "Bruce K", "Date": "on April 26, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great smart lighting system", "Text": "I love the Hue system. So much better than the Wemo system. However, now that I have the SmartThings hub, there are other bulbs that work. But the Hue system is very easy to use and is the most reliable smart lighting system that I have used."}
{"Author": "Garrett S Frisby", "Date": "on April 25, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "... because the bulbs both started getting hot and smelt like burning plastic", "Text": "Only took one star off because the bulbs both started getting hot and smelt like burning plastic. Switched them to different lamps and havent had it since. But still shouldn't of ever happened. Otherwise works well when synced with Alexa to turn on the lights."}
