{"Author": "Connor L", "Date": "on April 24, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Works great with alexa", "Text": "Works great with alexa. Heres a tip - If you manually turn off light and hur stops working, go on your phone and turn the lights off with hue app. It will reset the lights so they start working again"}
