{"Author": "Thomas swanson", "Date": "on March 13, 2017", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great Product. Really bad app from Phillips and watch the prices one supplier charges compared to another!", "Text": "It works great but the hub was not the newest generation hub which has not nor did not affect function in a bad way. Did not have any problems getting everything set up using the All 4 HUE app which is made by someone else and not by Philips.\n\nThe app that is made by Philips does not work at all and it is the 2nd worst app I've ever used. Philips did a really bad job with the app and they should have never put it out for use. If you get this do not use the app phillips tells you to use because it will not see any philips hubs or products. Infact I don't even thick the app could find itself if it wanted to.\n\nJust download the ALL 4 HUE app and forget about the philips app. The only other complaint other than the philips app is that most of philips hue things are getting expensive and I mean ridiculously expensive. Otherwise everything works great with the bulbs and hub. Setup with Alexa and the 3rd party hue app was seemless and very nice. Watch the prices though because you could spend any where from a good reasonable price to a price almost 100$ for the same thing.\n\nI'm giving this only 3 stars because the app phillips tells you to use does not work at all. So you have to use a 3rd party app called ALL 4 HUE and for the fact that you have to really watch out because some suppliers of phillips hue things on Amazon will gouge you for sometimes 100$ more than the next supplier."}
{"Author": "Tara L Barnes", "Date": "on March 13, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Light and Bright , love the ease of these.", "Text": "I use these with Alexa , and I love them. My porch light is all set and we have fixed the problem of my daughter being afraid to go in her dark room. My wifi reaches them great and I would love to put them outside , but unless well covered they don't work. Crazy easy to set up !"}
