{"Author": "jewelie", "Date": "on February 15, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great gift idea", "Text": "I ordered this as a gift for my brother. He received an Amazon Echo for Christmas and I thought this would be a great addition to a \"smart\" home. He really enjoyed getting this gift and I've seen him use it a bunch of times when his hands were full with the baby!"}
