{"Author": "Chuck Armstrong", "Date": "on January 25, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Loving it!!!!!", "Text": "Ok, first of all the set up was amazingly simple. I paired with my echo dot, and am loving it! I can turn off all the household lights from my bed using either Alexa, or the app on my phone. Bedroom, kitchen and living room lights all come on in the morning, when my alarm goes off, without fumbling for light switches in the dark; No more stubbed toes!!! Dim all the lights to watch a movie, or take a nap, in a snap! Total of five lights purchased so far and am already planning to add more."}
