{"Author": "Bob", "Date": "on January 10, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "These Are Great! Works With Samsung Smart Things", "Text": "Need more of these bulbs now. This is great for doing automated lighting. It works with the Samsung Smart Things home automation hub. I have my porch lights come on a half hour after sunset and turn off automatically. Or I can control them from anywhere. Setup was easy but it needs to be physically plugged in to your router. Works with Amazon Echo too."}
{"Author": "J. Gitzlaff", "Date": "on January 10, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Gets the job done, reliable", "Text": "I've been very happy with my kit. The white lights are easier to control and much more useful and economical than the colored ones anyway, and the base station is among the more reliable electronic appliances around my house. After months of use, I've never had to restart or reboot, which is more than I can say for my Airport Extreme or my Echo Dot units. As long as you attach yours in a good location so that its signal covers your entire living space, my experience is that the system should be reliable and rock solid."}
