{"Author": "Shu-Shu", "Date": "on January 8, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Easy and addictive", "Text": "I am not tech savvy. I bought the Alexa dot so that I could listen to music and find out about the weather. In learning about that I found out about these Hue lights. I liked the idea of having light go on and off and have trouble with the pain of timers on every plug. So I bought these. And love them. Super easy to set up. I use a couple of different apps. But when I come down in the morning the lights are on. If I come home after dark it is to amour up house. And I love telling Alexa to \"trigger bedtime\" on my ways up the stairs. I have more on order and can't wait to be able to turn the kids lights on in the morning or off at bedtime... if you are thinking about doing smart lighting this is the start up set I recommend. And I bought these at full price and was not bribed to give a review."}
