{"Author": "Brandon", "Date": "on January 5, 2017", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "They worked great.. While they lasted. Made In China.", "Text": "They worked great.. While they lasted. Made In China. The lights failed after only 4 months. They still receive a WiFi signal, but the light does not turn on. I paid about $15-20 for these lights and expected them to work much better. The product is great from the standpoint that they have an open API, but if I have to replace these bulbs every 4 months that is simply not doable. I am not going to buy more Hue products based on my experience with their products."}
