{"Author": "Lonny S Garris", "Date": "on January 5, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I found the system easy to set up", "Text": "I found the system easy to set up. Alexa was able to easily find one of the bulbs of the two. The other bulb was able to be manually turned on, just not by Alexa. I might try it again in the future, but the system is being returned to Amazon today."}
{"Author": "DONALD R WYNN", "Date": "on January 5, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Works as Expected and Easy to Setup", "Text": "I have tried several different lights with my Echo Dot and this is the best of all the options I tried. I expected the Plug In Unit to be universal in terms of industry and application but that is not the case. Sylvania bulbs will not work with a Phillips Hue plug in unit. I have ordered additional Philips bulbs and eagerly await their arrival."}
