{"Author": "Oz", "Date": "on January 4, 2017", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Not Ready For Prime Time", "Text": "Inconsistent and does not work well. White light bulb gets stuck on 10% brightness and can't be controlled by the Hue app. Rebooting the bridge multiple times helped. Mesh network is weak at best. I'll wait for the next generation if I were to buy again."}
