{"Author": "J. Jackson-Forsberg", "Date": "on January 2, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Switch to smart bulbs...you won't be disappointed", "Text": "I am so excited to introduce smart bulbs into my home! I have used these A19 bulbs in an antique lamp in my living room and a floor lamp in my bedroom. My Hue bulbs are paired with an Echo Dot. It's nice to be able to ask Alexa to turn on my living room lamp or dim it when we watch a movie. Turning on the lamp from across the room is arguably lazy. However, having dimmable bulbs that allow us to adjust the intensity of light rather than just switch the lamp on or off is a wonderful addition to any room! Plus, the estimated energy cost for each bulb is just over $1 per year."}
