{"Author": "PLK", "Date": "on December 24, 2016", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "it didn't connect to my network from away. The ...", "Text": "it didn't connect to my network from away. The only way to make it work from my own home network, what's the point. If I'm in my house I can just walk to my lamp and turn it up myself. Neither Alexa was able to find these lamps, even after I set it up in it apps, on Alexa and everywhere else I was asked. Phillip has a long way to go on this product"}
{"Author": "Timmy C Huynh", "Date": "on December 24, 2016", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Four Stars", "Text": "Easy to setup and nice option for a smart home. Five star if it weren't so expensive."}
