{"Author": "Kindle Customer", "Date": "on December 24, 2016", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Setup not easily understood", "Text": "I have an Alexa and I bought this to go with her. I followed the instructions and tried for days to get the hue bridge to connect using the app they have you download. I was giving up when I was thumbing through my Alexa app one day. Alexa had connected with the darn thing already and I didn't know it. Really bad instructions on getting it up and running, this could have ended with me returning the product."}
