{"Author": "BlueSky", "Date": "on December 19, 2016", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I Love My Hue Bulbs !!", "Text": "I love my Hue bulbs!!! I had trouble with the bridge always disconnecting until I moved it away from the stereo--it must have been getting interference. It's great to have the programmed settings for each room so that lights can come on when it gets dark if I am not home; I can set it so they go on as I approach home in a vehicle; and I can control my lights from anywhere, in home or out-of-home. It works great with its native app or with my iPhone Home app. Love this product."}
