{"Author": "ultra55371d", "Date": "on December 14, 2016", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Great Setup and Features for Echo", "Text": "We purchased this with a new Echo Dot and they work great together. Setup was very easy and took no more then 10 minutes. The color of the light is a little on the yellow side (I prefer 5k color of LED lights). There is a 1-3 second delay between giving the command to the echo to the lights doing the action. It was a little frustrating at first, but after a few days, we are used to it and very pleased with the performance off the lights and bridge with our new Dot. We use our new Echo setup with these lights in our Master Bedroom and Bathroom and the voice control has made things so convenient for us. We have them to automatically turn on in the morning and we are constantly using the dimming option throughout the day. This setup works great with Echo and I highly recommend them."}
{"Author": "Tim Yeh", "Date": "on December 14, 2016", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Valed starter kit with Amazon Echo.", "Text": "Easy to pair bulb with the hub. After activation, I use Amazon Echo to control them. Now I don't have to turn off the light and walk in the dark to sleep."}
{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on December 14, 2016", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Four Stars", "Text": "great gift"}
