{"Author": "Rikki Tissier", "Date": "on December 3, 2016", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Very easy setup", "Text": "Extremely easy to set up - screw in the bulbs, flip the switch, and let the app find the hub & lights. That's it!\n\nPersonally I enjoy using the Hue iOS app more than HomeKit (though I realize opinions are divided on this!). The schedules and geofencing are great.\n\nI've thoroughly enjoyed switching to smart lighting (I now have a dozen Hue bulbs), and this starter kit was my first foray into it."}
