{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on November 30, 2016", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Awesome product", "Text": "I don't normally take the time to write reviews, but this one is so good I had too! The install was really simple(aside from their being 2 apps in the App Store and not getting the right one on first download). Once I had the right app installed the bridge paired and I was able to control the lights. I have one in my front door and one in my living room. A little app configuration and I had it setup to turn on the lights when I come home(and it's dark), and turn them off when I leave. It's so awesome not being in the dark trying to unlock the door anymore. I even connected it to my Amazon echo so can voice control the lights"}
